      "rationale": "Code verification at Gradation 3 requires method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) testing for the governing equations relevant to this COU (incompressible Navier-Stokes with non-Newtonian viscosity and power-law hemolysis model). MMS tests were executed for all three modules with observed order of accuracy within 5% of theoretical.",
