      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study with GCI methodology (Celik et al. 2008) was performed. GCI fine < 2.1% for velocity and < 3.8% for hemolysis index across all five operating points. Apparent order of accuracy 1.97. Exceeds Gradation 3 requirement; assessed at Gradation 4 due to systematic Richardson extrapolation and uncertainty bounding on all QoIs.",
