      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions for the FDA benchmark PIV study are fully documented including fluid properties (blood analog, viscosity, density), pump geometry (certified to FDA specification), flow rates (calibrated Coriolis meters ±0.5%), and rotational speed (encoder ±1 RPM). Boundary conditions in CFD replicate experimental conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
